    "body": "This is definitely reproducible on OS X with Chrome 33 and Firefox 28.  But I'm worried that it sometimes seems to work \"correctly\" -- that is, it occasionally just moves by one _apparent_ line, but then goes back to _actual_ lines.  I've been keeping up with HEAD, and I've only noticed this in the past couple days.  I really don't like the idea of hard wrapping, unless maybe there's an auto-rewrap function.\n"
